Notable players.
During the club's centenary season, a "<a href="Hall%20of%20Fame">Hall of Fame</a>" was created, honouring 100 former players chosen by fan vote. Further players have since been inducted into the Norwich City Hall of Fame.
Greatest Ever Norwich City XI (1902–2008).
In 2008, supporters cast votes to determine the greatest ever Norwich City team.
Players of the Season.
Every year, fans vote for whom they believe to have been the player of the season.
