Performance record of clubs in the Premier League

 
Since inception in 1992 there have been 50 clubs who have played in the <a href="Premier%20League">Premier League</a>. Seven clubs have won the Premier League: <a href="Manchester%20United%20F.C.">Manchester United</a> (13 times), <a href="Manchester%20City%20F.C.">Manchester City</a> (seven times), <a href="Chelsea%20F.C.">Chelsea</a> (five times), <a href="Arsenal%20F.C.">Arsenal</a> (three times), <a href="Blackburn%20Rovers%20F.C.">Blackburn Rovers</a> (once), <a href="Leicester%20City%20F.C.">Leicester City</a> (once) and <a href="Liverpool%20F.C.">Liverpool</a> (once).
